snippet.title: Mega Man Battle Chip Challenge - Part 2: Guts Class
snippet.description:
You can support both Mega Man AND me through Nexus: https://www.nexus.gg/megaquint
 As the title suggests, the last one we fight is Guts Man. It also has an actual fee so we do need some money to get in. __

If you want to send a tip: www.paypal.me/MegaQuint
You can also follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/megaquint I don't post much, but here I am.
